  schema:name "General Relativity" ;
  schema:description "General relativity is Einstein's theory of gravity (1915), in which the geometry of [spacetime](./spacetime.md) is determined by the distribution of mass and energy, and the geometry of spacetime in turn determines how matter moves." ;
